1
00:01:25,317 --> 00:01:29,522
=Fights Break Sphere=

2
00:01:40,689 --> 00:01:42,859
=Episode 2=

3
00:01:44,700 --> 00:01:46,636
What is the reason
for giving me such a precious gift?

4
00:01:46,636 --> 00:01:49,706
May Brother Gu clarify it.

5
00:01:49,706 --> 00:01:53,409
Nalan Clan Leader and me are very good friends.

6
00:01:53,409 --> 00:01:56,312
Recently, I noticed that he is deeply troubled
by something and unable to sleep at night.

7
00:01:56,312 --> 00:01:58,081
Something is weighing heavily
on the Nalan Elder's mind,

8
00:01:58,081 --> 00:02:00,984
just what is it?

9
00:02:00,984 --> 00:02:06,088
It's concerning the Nalan descendants.

10
00:02:06,088 --> 00:02:09,526
Nalan Jie has three sons,
one weak and the other two are reckless.

11
00:02:09,526 --> 00:02:12,862
In the entire family, there is only

12
00:02:12,862 --> 00:02:16,966
one Nalan Yanran who is very smart
and is deeply favored by her grandfather.

13
00:02:16,966 --> 00:02:18,968
If Nalan Yanran gets married off to here,

14
00:02:18,968 --> 00:02:22,138
who then will be left to inherit

15
00:02:22,138 --> 00:02:24,507
the huge asset of the Nalan Clan?

16
00:02:24,507 --> 00:02:29,278
Elder Nalan finds our Xiao Clan unreliable now.

17
00:02:29,278 --> 00:02:30,614
He wants to cancel the engagement?

18
00:02:34,417 --> 00:02:36,486
He asked you to come to be the mediator.

19
00:02:38,587 --> 00:02:41,558
What Brother Xiao said is exactly right.

20
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:48,698
Your son is just a medicine shop apprentice

21
00:02:48,698 --> 00:02:51,200
and you've lost all your Fight Qi energy.

22
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:53,869
In the whole young generation of the Xiao Clan,
there's already no one

23
00:02:53,869 --> 00:02:56,206
that can be entrusted.

24
00:02:56,206 --> 00:02:58,474
If Nalan Yanran marries off to here,

25
00:02:58,474 --> 00:03:01,344
it will surely be of no benefit to the Nalan Clan.

26
00:03:01,344 --> 00:03:03,546
Then about the marriage
why don't we just cancel it?

27
00:03:05,448 --> 00:03:10,286
May Xiao Clan Leader personally bring up this topic.

28
00:03:10,286 --> 00:03:13,355
You also know that Elder Nalan is a person
that puts too much importance on his reputation.

29
00:03:13,355 --> 00:03:15,692
He doesn't want to end up with a bad name of
being heartless, not righteous, and breaking one's promise.

30
00:03:19,429 --> 00:03:22,098
He doesn't want to bear such bad name?

31
00:03:22,098 --> 00:03:24,334
What then does he want my Xiao Clan to say?

32
00:03:24,334 --> 00:03:27,536
Is is that he wants me to say
that my Xiao family is done for

33
00:03:27,536 --> 00:03:29,972
and that we're not good enough
for the Nalan clan?

34
00:03:29,972 --> 00:03:33,876
This engagement was set
by our Xiao family ancestor.

35
00:03:33,876 --> 00:03:35,778
I'm unable to say those words.

36
00:03:35,778 --> 00:03:39,081
If I say it out, I will wrong

37
00:03:39,081 --> 00:03:42,652
my ancestors.

38
00:03:42,652 --> 00:03:44,954
Brother Xiao, forgive me for being frank.

39
00:03:44,954 --> 00:03:48,324
You need to be realistic.

40
00:03:48,324 --> 00:03:51,861
If you take a step back,
you would benefit rather than be reckless about it.

41
00:03:51,861 --> 00:03:56,265
If you take this pill,
you would gain back 60-70% of your Fight Qi energy.

42
00:03:56,265 --> 00:04:00,236
Some of the problems you do understand

43
00:04:00,236 --> 00:04:04,207
that there is still a big difference from
being a medicine shop owner to being a Fight Practitioner.

44
00:04:04,207 --> 00:04:06,109
That is reality.

45
00:04:10,180 --> 00:04:13,482
Although this pill is very good,

46
00:04:13,482 --> 00:04:17,319
using my son's lifelong happiness to exchange for it,

47
00:04:17,319 --> 00:04:19,355
using the thousand year old reputation
of Xiao Clan to exchange for it,

48
00:04:19,355 --> 00:04:21,091
don't you think that it's too little?

49
00:04:22,592 --> 00:04:24,260
You really underestimate the Xiao family.

50
00:04:32,102 --> 00:04:36,606
Brother Gu, please let the Nalan Elder know

51
00:04:36,606 --> 00:04:38,808
that if he wants to cancel the engagement,

52
00:04:38,808 --> 00:04:43,145
please come and tell me himself.
If he doesn't,

53
00:04:43,145 --> 00:04:46,149
then the engagement is on.

54
00:04:57,793 --> 00:04:58,795
I'll take my leave.

55
00:05:20,517 --> 00:05:23,820
Congratulations, Elder Xiao.

56
00:05:23,820 --> 00:05:26,022
This way, please.

57
00:05:26,022 --> 00:05:27,390
Congratulations, Elder Xiao.

58
00:05:27,390 --> 00:05:29,392
Please, please come in.

59
00:05:29,392 --> 00:05:32,162
Please have a seat.

60
00:05:36,833 --> 00:05:41,070
Xiao Yan, you should offer a cup of tea

61
00:05:41,070 --> 00:05:45,241
to Elder Nalan.

62
00:05:46,443 --> 00:05:48,011
Once you've become his grandson-in-law,
you must be more respectful to him.

63
00:05:48,011 --> 00:05:49,380
Yes.

64
00:05:55,519 --> 00:05:58,689
Grandfather, let me give you a toast.

65
00:06:06,763 --> 00:06:10,601
Grandfather, let me give you a toast.

66
00:06:22,746 --> 00:06:25,683
Grandfather.

67
00:06:27,484 --> 00:06:28,786
Let me give you a toast.

68
00:06:41,031 --> 00:06:44,201
Xiao Yan, wait until grandpa finishes speaking

69
00:06:44,201 --> 00:06:46,737
before drinking the wine.

70
00:06:49,205 --> 00:06:51,475
The Nalan Clan is on the decline.

71
00:06:53,477 --> 00:06:57,080
Elder Nalan, you shouldn't say that.

72
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:59,650
Today's a happy occasion.

73
00:06:59,650 --> 00:07:02,319
As long as our two families can be united . . .

74
00:07:05,222 --> 00:07:09,460
Brother Xiao, the Nalan clan is on the decline.

75
00:07:11,829 --> 00:07:15,399
I'm 79-years-old this year. I'm old.

76
00:07:17,568 --> 00:07:20,771
In the generation of Yanran's father,
there wasn't any talented standout.

77
00:07:22,372 --> 00:07:24,208
I only have this one granddaughter.

78
00:07:25,975 --> 00:07:28,512
She can be considered to have talented attributes.

79
00:07:30,981 --> 00:07:34,185
Seven years ago,
in the distant expedition to the Soul Hall,

80
00:08:15,959 --> 00:08:18,061
all the elite Fight Practitioners
that our Nalan Clan sent

81
00:08:18,061 --> 00:08:21,198
didn't return.

82
00:08:21,198 --> 00:08:26,203
The son remaining is crippled.

83
00:08:26,203 --> 00:08:29,406
In such a huge family asset,
if you're going to look at it closely,

84
00:08:29,406 --> 00:08:32,342
it's just an empty shell.

85
00:08:32,342 --> 00:08:36,046
Thinking about the danger
that I have to face in the future,

86
00:08:36,046 --> 00:08:38,716
I'm unable to sleep, Little Brother Xiao.

87
00:08:41,618 --> 00:08:45,723
The five great clans must unite
and also preserve oneself.

88
00:08:45,723 --> 00:08:49,124
There's no getting around this.

89
00:08:49,124 --> 00:08:51,761
My granddaughter, Yanran,

90
00:08:53,263 --> 00:08:56,333
is the Nalan clan's last hope.

91
00:08:56,333 --> 00:08:58,602
She must find someone more dependable.

92
00:09:00,804 --> 00:09:04,474
She cannot be married to Xiao Yan.

93
00:09:04,474 --> 00:09:05,709
This... How come he's just
taking it back like that?

94
00:09:05,709 --> 00:09:08,178
Indeed. That is so unreasonable.

95
00:09:08,178 --> 00:09:10,480
What now then? This is so preposterous.

96
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:14,151
Makes people mad.

97
00:09:14,151 --> 00:09:15,886
I'll return the betrothal gifts of the Xiao Clan
at 10 times the original amount.

98
00:09:18,488 --> 00:09:23,427
Today's banquet is not an engagement banquet.
It's to form an alliance.

99
00:09:23,427 --> 00:09:28,031
From this day forth, all of the Xiao family

100
00:09:28,031 --> 00:09:31,101
will be under the protection of the Nalan clan.

101
00:09:31,101 --> 00:09:34,304
If anyone has issues with the Xiao family,

102
00:09:34,304 --> 00:09:37,074
I will be the first one
who won't let that person get away.

103
00:09:41,211 --> 00:09:43,580
Elder Nalan holds high position and power.
Having such sense of responsibility towards one's friend

104
00:09:43,580 --> 00:09:45,883
is quite rare.

105
00:09:58,095 --> 00:10:01,765
This was the engagement agreement.

106
00:10:01,765 --> 00:10:04,935
Please save me some face and take it back.

107
00:10:19,917 --> 00:10:25,288
Uncle Xiao, in a matter like canceling a marriage agreement,
someone must take responsibility.

108
00:10:25,288 --> 00:10:27,123
If not because we want to
maintain the reputation of the Xiao Clan,

109
00:10:27,123 --> 00:10:28,792
my grandfather would have forced the cancellation.

110
00:10:32,195 --> 00:10:37,067
Xiao Yan, if you want to preserve your family's prestige,

111
00:10:37,067 --> 00:10:40,103
we can see about this arrangement in three years.
In three years,

112
00:10:40,103 --> 00:10:42,005
you can come to the Cloud Mist Sect
and challenge me.

113
00:10:42,005 --> 00:10:45,008
If you win, I'll be at your service.

114
00:10:58,721 --> 00:11:02,625
There's no need to wait three years.
Nalan Yanran,

115
00:11:02,625 --> 00:11:05,095
I'm already not interested in you.

116
00:11:16,639 --> 00:11:18,775
Looks like this engagement cup of wine

117
00:11:18,775 --> 00:11:20,411
won't have anyone to drink it.

118
00:11:21,444 --> 00:11:22,646
It's fine.

119
00:11:24,681 --> 00:11:28,585
Then let's all drink
to cancelling the engagement.

120
00:11:30,554 --> 00:11:32,556
"xiu"

121
00:11:34,391 --> 00:11:35,793
It's the Nalan clan
that's not good enough for our Xiao family.

122
00:11:39,596 --> 00:11:40,697
Grandfather.

123
00:11:44,668 --> 00:11:46,069
Do as you wish.

124
00:11:51,107 --> 00:11:53,276
Xiao Yan.

125
00:11:53,276 --> 00:11:56,280
Explain to me,

126
00:11:56,280 --> 00:11:58,748
what's the meaning of this word?

127
00:11:58,748 --> 00:12:01,317
This word is "xiu"

128
00:12:01,317 --> 00:12:03,453
because this engagement

129
00:12:03,453 --> 00:12:06,522
means that Yanran is my wife.

130
00:12:06,522 --> 00:12:08,926
Now that the word "xiu" is added,

131
00:12:08,926 --> 00:12:11,361
so she is no longer my wife.

132
00:12:11,361 --> 00:12:13,463
She hasn't married yet,

133
00:12:13,463 --> 00:12:15,365
how can you mention that word?

134
00:12:15,365 --> 00:12:19,068
This engagement was arranged by my grandfather.

135
00:12:19,068 --> 00:12:23,172
You also signed your name in this marriage agreement.
My parents have given the betrothal gifts since we were little.

136
00:12:23,172 --> 00:12:24,641
It also has the Yanran and my birthdates.

137
00:12:26,610 --> 00:12:27,744
How can you say that she isn't married yet?

138
00:12:31,281 --> 00:12:37,487
This word . . . you just want to ruin Yanran.

139
00:12:37,487 --> 00:12:39,723
It's you who first wanted to
ruin the Xiao family's reputation.

140
00:12:39,723 --> 00:12:41,525
I want you to eat this paper!

141
00:12:43,526 --> 00:12:46,063
Xiao Yan, apologize now.

142
00:12:59,042 --> 00:13:00,177
Elder.

143
00:13:00,177 --> 00:13:01,745
Elder!

144
00:13:10,786 --> 00:13:15,025
Xiao Yan, I can make the whole Xiao Clan
crawl out of Wu Tan City.

145
00:13:15,025 --> 00:13:17,094
Yanran, make him eat his words.

146
00:13:40,917 --> 00:13:45,289
Xiao Yan, Grandfather wants you to eat it,
so eat it.

147
00:14:14,284 --> 00:14:18,721
Elder Xiao, are you happy
that things have come to this?

148
00:14:18,721 --> 00:14:21,291
Your son has no discipline

149
00:14:23,894 --> 00:14:28,865
Xiao Yan, if you want to marry the girl,
you have to be able to protect the family.

150
00:14:28,865 --> 00:14:32,268
You can't even block her one move.
I think with this divorce paper...

151
00:14:32,268 --> 00:14:33,870
It should be Yanran
who should be cancelling the engagement, not you.

152
00:14:54,391 --> 00:14:56,893
Yanran, stop it.

153
00:15:10,673 --> 00:15:12,109
Son!

154
00:15:27,457 --> 00:15:28,692
Son.

155
00:15:30,327 --> 00:15:31,895
Nalan Yanran.

156
00:15:41,404 --> 00:15:44,374
Three years.

157
00:15:44,374 --> 00:15:48,145
In three years, I will challenge you to a fight

158
00:15:49,612 --> 00:15:50,881
At that time,

159
00:15:53,183 --> 00:15:54,251
for the insults you threw upon the Xiao family,

160
00:15:55,952 --> 00:15:57,754
I will in the same way,

161
00:15:59,355 --> 00:16:01,692
pay it back to you in the same manner.

162
00:16:02,792 --> 00:16:04,127
Remember this.

163
00:16:06,796 --> 00:16:09,733
The river flows east for 30 years.

164
00:16:09,733 --> 00:16:12,936
It'll flow west for 30 years as well.

165
00:16:20,476 --> 00:16:22,212
Don't belittle
or take advantage of a disadvantaged young person!

166
00:17:31,515 --> 00:17:35,385
Father, I will definitely make them pay.

167
00:17:57,773 --> 00:17:59,809
This is the Nalan clan's medicine.

168
00:17:59,809 --> 00:18:01,378
You can give it to Uncle Xiao.

169
00:18:16,559 --> 00:18:17,928
[Seven Years Ago, the funeral of Gu Wenxin]

170
00:18:27,437 --> 00:18:30,706
I heard that you won the championship.

171
00:18:30,706 --> 00:18:33,476
I made this for you.

172
00:18:33,476 --> 00:18:34,511
I'm giving it to you.

173
00:18:57,700 --> 00:18:58,602
Do you regret it?

174
00:19:00,537 --> 00:19:03,272
Who are you?

175
00:19:03,272 --> 00:19:05,274
Of course, I'm part of the Xiao family.

176
00:19:05,274 --> 00:19:09,111
I've parted ways with the Xiao family.

177
00:19:09,111 --> 00:19:11,413
If there's anyone in the Xiao Clan
that will stand out and talk,

178
00:19:11,413 --> 00:19:14,050
it will never be your turn, right?

179
00:19:14,050 --> 00:19:18,621
You want to cancel the marriage
because you think Xiao Yan is useless.

180
00:19:18,621 --> 00:19:20,457
He's not compatible with a precious heiress like you.

181
00:19:23,392 --> 00:19:26,596
When he was 9, he already was able to
create a level 9 Fight Qi Skills. What about you?

182
00:19:29,732 --> 00:19:32,102
He was able to create a miracle 7 years ago.

183
00:19:33,636 --> 00:19:35,138
In the future,

184
00:19:36,673 --> 00:19:39,776
what makes you think he can't make a comeback?

185
00:19:39,776 --> 00:19:42,878
Xiao Yan and I will meet again three years from now.

186
00:19:42,878 --> 00:19:46,583
In three years, if he can beat me,
I'll be at his service.

187
00:19:48,417 --> 00:19:51,888
In those three years, you're not in it.

188
00:19:51,888 --> 00:19:54,457
Move aside.

189
00:19:54,457 --> 00:19:56,493
Don't think that because you have
the Cloud Mist Sect as your Nalan Clan's backer,

190
00:19:56,493 --> 00:19:57,961
you can run amuck.

191
00:19:59,362 --> 00:20:02,732
The Fight Qi Continent is so vast.

192
00:20:02,732 --> 00:20:05,435
There are so many sects stronger
than Cloud Mist Sect. You'll regret this.

193
00:20:31,661 --> 00:20:32,963
Take it.

194
00:20:35,364 --> 00:20:37,133
What is it I'm taking?

195
00:20:37,133 --> 00:20:39,703
It's not poison.It's for internal injuries.

196
00:20:45,141 --> 00:20:46,743
You're driving me crazy.

197
00:20:49,245 --> 00:20:52,048
Once I've become outstanding,
I'll let Nalan Yanran eat paper for fun.

198
00:20:53,916 --> 00:20:56,752
What are you saying?

199
00:20:56,752 --> 00:20:59,522
If father hears that,
he'll scold you again.

200
00:20:59,522 --> 00:21:00,423
Aren't you afraid
that you won't get married off in the future?

201
00:21:01,857 --> 00:21:05,261
I'm not getting married.

202
00:21:05,261 --> 00:21:08,731
I was about to tell father
that I don't want to learn Fight Qi anymore.

203
00:21:08,731 --> 00:21:10,100
I want to go to the medicine shop
and learn how to use the abacus.

204
00:21:11,634 --> 00:21:12,702
What did you say?

205
00:21:15,939 --> 00:21:19,743
Think about it. It's so boring for me
to learn Fight Qi alone.

206
00:21:24,246 --> 00:21:25,749
How can you be alone?

207
00:21:29,619 --> 00:21:30,687
Aren't there a lot of other training disciples?

208
00:21:34,958 --> 00:21:37,893
How about this then? I'll go learn
to use the abacus in the medicine shop,

209
00:21:37,893 --> 00:21:41,330
while you cut the herbs.
This way, we can be together every day.

210
00:21:41,330 --> 00:21:44,134
It's too boring to learn Fight Qi with them.

211
00:21:52,775 --> 00:21:55,311
You should go back.

212
00:21:57,647 --> 00:21:59,682
You better remove that idea
from your head right now. Go back and sleep.

213
00:22:01,117 --> 00:22:03,086
Father will never agree. Go now.

214
00:22:06,456 --> 00:22:08,058
I'll visit you once you're happier then.

215
00:22:41,691 --> 00:22:45,095
Grand Old Master.

216
00:22:46,763 --> 00:22:47,730
Grand Old Master.

217
00:23:10,019 --> 00:23:11,822
Have you thought it through?

218
00:23:12,422 --> 00:23:14,291
If I drink more wine,
your butt will have to suffer a beating again.

219
00:23:16,893 --> 00:23:19,295
My butt already has calluses from the beating.

220
00:23:19,295 --> 00:23:20,497
There's no difference getting hit again.

221
00:23:22,499 --> 00:23:24,768
Drink up. Just think of it as my treat.

222
00:23:30,272 --> 00:23:32,809
Where are you at now?

223
00:23:34,176 --> 00:23:38,014
Level 3.

224
00:23:39,282 --> 00:23:42,118
Three years.

225
00:23:42,718 --> 00:23:45,921
Even if you're given 30 years before going back
to find that lady from the Nalan Clan, it's useless.

226
00:23:45,921 --> 00:23:48,591
Her teacher is Yun Shan.

227
00:23:48,591 --> 00:23:50,359
So in three years,
how much do you think you'll improve?

228
00:23:50,359 --> 00:23:52,361
You know about it?

229
00:23:52,361 --> 00:23:54,697
Even if I don't want to know,
I have no choice.

230
00:23:54,697 --> 00:23:58,034
Those harsh words were like
awls piercing through my ears.

231
00:23:59,401 --> 00:24:02,238
Nalan Jie, that old man

232
00:24:02,238 --> 00:24:05,741
is so snobbish and narrow-minded.
If I'm still alive

233
00:24:05,741 --> 00:24:08,978
and I went to drink your celebratory wine,
even if he's given 10 more guts,

234
00:24:08,978 --> 00:24:10,413
he wouldn't dare say anything
about canceling the wedding.

235
00:24:12,348 --> 00:24:16,119
Cut it out. Stop bragging.

236
00:24:16,119 --> 00:24:19,522
Also, there's no point in whatever you say.

237
00:24:19,522 --> 00:24:24,026
This engagement banquet of mine

238
00:24:24,026 --> 00:24:26,295
was really so embarrassing to the point that the
mother of shame had to open the shame doors for me.

239
00:24:26,295 --> 00:24:29,899
What did you say?

240
00:24:29,899 --> 00:24:31,667
Being embarrassed to the point of reaching home.
(Shameful to the highest level.)

241
00:24:31,667 --> 00:24:35,037
You're something. After experiencing
such a huge setback, you still can smile.

242
00:24:35,037 --> 00:24:38,041
Or else what?

243
00:24:38,041 --> 00:24:42,145
Must I live my life with tears on my face
every day and be in utter pain?

244
00:24:42,145 --> 00:24:44,915
Why don't I just look for a rope and hang myself here?

245
00:24:47,083 --> 00:24:49,987
Everyone has Fight Qi Skills.

246
00:24:49,987 --> 00:24:53,924
But you have to condense them into a whirl of qi and convert
into Fight Qi before you can become a Fight Practitioner.

247
